name: ① NEW CREATIVE CYCLE
description:
The mystical creatures within the depths of AVA UNIVERSE want to help and guide you through your troubles or questions（✿ ͡◕ ᴗ◕)つ━━✫・*。 

Thank you to the collective energy of the HEN Witches a temporary portal between the depths of AVA UNIVERSE and the physical realm opened. 

Take advantage of this time to thank your higher-self for bringing you in a path of creativity... and to think this is only the beginning! 


.。･:*:･ BY BEING A CARD HOLDER YOU WILL RECEIVE A PERSONALIZED CARD READING .。･:*:･ 

You can choose between:
(1) Virtual Session (15-30min Google Meet ~ DM me @ava_digitalart on Twitter to schedule a time!)
(2) Chat Session (If you're a lil shy or are super busy ~ DM me @ava_digitalart on Twitter)
